reviews.customers_say: Customers find the sweater well-made with a nice collar that elevates its style, and one mentions it's dressy enough to wear with a skirt. They appreciate its softness, comfort, and true-to-size fit, with one noting it's not too scratchy. Customers like the color, with one mentioning it doesn't fade or bleed, and they appreciate its medium weight.

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars A favorite
items.body: Can’t say enough about this sweater. Soft and warm and washes great. Fit is just right too with the sleeve length long enough to cover my wrists. I have already purchased it in another color and might just buy another one. Great with jeans but dressy enough with a skirt. Read more
items.author: Jozlyn Klettlinger

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars It has a high quality feel.
items.body: I ordered three is these sweaters for gifts. They arrived late and I planned on returning them. Needing a sweater for an event, I tried one on and I now own all three. First, it has the perfect weight, not too heavy or too light, perfect to keep you warm during the winter months, and perfect for spring when weather is cooler. The V neck sits just right, not too low. The accent buttons are a nice touch. The collar lays nicely , it does not scratch or feel cumbersome. The ribbing texture has a nice feel and look. I normally wear a medium and it is true to size. If you like things more fitted, I would downsize. This sweater feels high quality and I have received many compliments when I wear them. I have the off white, blue, and pink. They have become my favorite sweaters. Read more
items.author: Betsy Neubauer

items.body: Seems nice, but runs large. I will be returning. I ordered a small, I typically wear a small - I am 5 2", 124 lbs. Read more

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Pretty Fall Sweater!
items.body: Very pretty sweater that XL fit perfect. I usually take large/XL and glad I went with XL for this sweater. I have had several good comments on it - may seem a little wild at first, but the color and fabric is so nice for the Fall and looks great with jeans or dressier pants. Happy with my purchase! items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Value for money
items.body: Wanted a warm trendy sweater top and I am absolutely pleased with my purchase. The fit is what I expected and the material is soft and comfy. Highly recommended Read more

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Comfortable, fits great, rich colors
items.body: Love this sweater so much I bought it in 2 colors - caramel and dark green. Colors are just as pictured. Sweater is comfortable, not bulky, and does not need a shirt underneath. Washes well, colors don't fade/bleed, and does not need ironing. Travels well, too. Read more

short_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is made for a polished look that still feels comfortable to wear. It is designed to sit cleanly on the body with a flattering shape that works for day plans and dressier moments without feeling overdone.

The fit focuses on balance rather than extremes, so you can move naturally while still getting a defined silhouette. Choose your usual size for a closer look, or size up if you prefer a little more ease through the waist and hips.

Styling is simple: keep accessories minimal for a clean finish, or add a jacket and statement shoes when you want a sharper outfit. This piece photographs well thanks to smooth lines and a structured feel that stays put once you have it adjusted.

With the right fit and simple styling, this item becomes an easy go-to when you want something that looks intentional without requiring extra effort.

To keep it looking sharp, follow the care label first and avoid high heat when drying or steaming if the material is sensitive.

The design is easy to style with simple accessories and works well in photos thanks to clean lines and a balanced silhouette.

long_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is a versatile piece you can reach for when you want a put-together look that still feels comfortable. The goal is simple: a silhouette that reads polished, photographs well, and stays wearable for a full day or a long night.

Fit and sizing Fit is where most outfits win or lose. This design aims for a balanced shape with a defined line through the torso, a clean waist, and a smooth finish through the hips and legs. If you prefer a more relaxed feel, size up; if you like a closer fit, stay true to size. Sizes may include: XS, S, M, L, XL.

Fabric and comfort Comfort is not just about softness. It is also about movement and how the fabric behaves as you walk, sit, and stand. A fabric blend with a bit of give helps it keep its shape while still feeling wearable.

Highlights A clean neckline and a refined silhouette for an elevated look. Designed to layer easily with jackets, wraps, or sweaters. Works well with both minimal accessories and statement pieces.

How to style Styling ideas: keep it minimal with neutral shoes and one standout accessory. For a relaxed daytime look, add a denim jacket or cardigan. For events, switch to a bolder shoe and a small clutch for a sharper finish.

Color notes Available colors may include: Apricot Black Stripes, Nutmeg, Camel White Stripes, Grey Blue, Army Green, Black and White, Black, Coffee, Dark Gray, White and Burgundy, Red Snowflakes, Apricot Floral, White and Khaki, Deep Purple. If a shade is sold out, check back as availability can change.

Care Care guidance matters if you want it to keep its shape and finish. Follow the label first.
